data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath in NW Bakersfield, It is amazingly well kept and clean as a whistle. Walk in through the front door and you'll immediately feel the warmth and peacefulness that a home should provide. master suite with walk=in closets, soaking tub, The kitchen is just beautiful, stainless steel appliances, and a very useful center island. newer paint and carpet. cozy fireplace in the family room, beautiful pool with water falls to enjoy those hot summer days. Great schools, shopping, and restaurants are just a hop, skip, and a jump away.
